column2: SELECT TOP # objid, p.dered_r, ra, dec, p.petror9#_r, p.dered_g, p_el_mon as elliptical, p_cw_mon as spiralclock, p_acw_mon as spiralanticlock FROM Galaxy as p JOIN zooMonochromeBias ON objid = objid JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE zns.p_cw> # or zns.p_acw> # or zns.p_el> #
